{"tid":549834,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佩爾：歡迎馬列斯回來","createTime":"2018-02-04T05:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T12:13:34.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d30c71ee3de16486db85b7ea93c5276fdf23ec2","tid":549834,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=DnNAoCEY61nQzabBFrNAfNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c08fca75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】雖然在轉會窗關閉前要求離隊不果的馬列斯繼續缺陣，但李斯特城領隊佩爾大方地表示，歡迎這名翼鋒回來。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的翼鋒馬列斯（Riyad Mahrez）為了轉投曼城，早前連日來都缺操，繼周中英超後，於周六對史雲斯的聯賽繼續缺陣，連後備席也不見其身影。<br />\n<br />\n佩爾在賽後再次談及這名阿爾及利亞國腳：「球員會歡迎馬列斯回來，他毫無疑問是我們的最佳球員。現在的情況要由他、他的經理人、球會去處理，但我們一定會歡迎他歸隊。」<br />\n<br />\n沒有馬列斯在陣中，李斯特城連續第2場失分，今戰主場以1:1賽和榜尾史雲斯，佩爾坦言失望：「我們有足夠的機會去取得多於1球。我不認為賽和是一個公平的戰果，我們失了2分。恭喜史雲斯，但我們值得獲勝。」"},{"pid":"f15f6b50fd1a0592e4f42da1ff3f4d74b015c3d9","tid":549834,"uid":72415,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0bae0337ad3f5f7d08acf947bb44d1b61053d5a","tid":549834,"uid":8883,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/135639_828608f67fdc2683e4db0b96dbce49df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F135639_828608f67fdc2683e4db0b96dbce49df.png&h=9536132e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"286b136194bc9a559bca0149227c39d175c7187e","tid":549834,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:57:00.000Z","msg":"冇紀律既球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再好波有咩用"},{"pid":"8730ccbf0bc7a1943cccded7b833024d78813938","tid":549834,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"尋晚柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd2182f66b4c21a7dce23b5bb13669095b45a1c","tid":549834,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"65M都唔放<br />\n球員hea踢<br />\n又何必呢<br />\nps.馬列斯全盛時侯可以離隊幾多次，每次都走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12982713d21cff5226ce0b2e3878f90ce6f2a3a","tid":549834,"uid":34490,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0bae0337ad3f5f7d08acf947bb44d1b61053d5a","tid":549834,"uid":8883,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/135639_828608f67fdc2683e4db0b96dbce49df.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F135639_828608f67fdc2683e4db0b96dbce49df.png&h=9536132e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe651bc4146b52b650c2076fa6d5bfc11e94361","tid":549834,"uid":53238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"李城損人不利己<br />\n出到 65M 自己又冇野爭都唔賣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3a6f41ced51a9d2ff2c0dbf7c01c2e845e70b8","tid":549834,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"9xm 大貪左d囉"}]}